modShortDescription: This mod adds new turrets & traps. Each turret & trap has a schematic that can be found in loot. Dart Turret, Heavy Turret, Whirlwind and Shellshock.
modDescription:
This mod adds new turrets & [traps](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-traps/). Each turret & trap has a schematic that can be found in loot.

## Traps

* Dart Turret \[Shoots Iron Darts | +Fire-Rate | +Durability\]
* Heavy Turret \[Shoots 7.62mm Ammo | +Fire-Rate | +Damage | +Durability\]
* Whirlwind \[Super Blade Trap | 2x1x2 Placement | Shocks on hit | +Damage | +Durability\]
* Shellshock \[Super Electric Fence |1x1x1 Placement | Shocks & Burns on hit | +Damage | +Durability\]

**[Download](https://www.dropbox.com/s/vrwsn495ebqk345/CJ%27s%20Super%20Traps.rar?dl=1)**
